dBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:56:35.000Z","msg":"食得幾日, 有效藥都無咁快見效啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4426151cd63466f99081331d8c821034360938","tid":179933,"uid":44039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:58:20.000Z","msg":"避孕藥唔係即食即有效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主或者條仔google下都知咩事<br />\n身體係自己 由得條仔話點就點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622e54b05783fc155c016bdcb8afa47515ab2ef6","tid":179933,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:10:13.000Z","msg":"媽咪唔好唔要我呀"},{"pid":"8b50765826a779f5fd4ceebecb332b325bcbe481","tid":179933,"uid":16642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咩叫無藥效果幾粒</blockquote><br />\n因為一個cycle係28日<br />\n咁正常黎M嗰幾日唔洗食<br />\n但係一停左食之後就會好容易唔記得食<br />\n所以有幾粒會係普通維他命黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學到野<br />\n咁係用顏色/大細/形狀黎分?</blockquote><br />\n好似顏色唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過而家好多都係就咁21粒算</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要睇咩牌子<br />\n21粒/28粒 藥份大致差唔多<br />\n只不過多左7粒係無藥份既糖衣藥<br />\n因為個7日係唔使食<br />\n<br />\n正常由你第一日開始食個日計7日（保險d有人預14日）先有避孕功效<br />\n<br />\n大多牌子都有箭咀指住好難睇錯<br />\n<br />\n好多牌子唔同價錢只在於單一激素定幾種激素"},{"pid":"699906700f2692f337947148ecab4bc424a491d2","tid":179933,"uid":70742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"你第1日m 到後第幾日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果頭7-9 都還可以的<br />\n<br />\n同你真係sure 你食左冇荷爾蒙的果幾粒？"},{"pid":"00289ae3f54c1378223de4afa4c71d651454b516","tid":179933,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T10:33:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你第1日m 到後第幾日食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果頭7-9 都還可以的<br />\