就得，例如你應該每日10pm食，但你早訓左，到第二日起身9am先記得，咁仲係12小時內，就可以一起身就食返，然後個日既10pm都照常食，咁樣仍然有避孕效果，但如果超過12小時先記得，咁你個粒可以唔使食，直接食每日10pm個粒，但就冇左避孕效果(未來7日)<br />\n利申:讀藥 <br />\n有咩唔明可以再問</blockquote><br />\n再利申，我係以oral combined contraceptive 28days 黎做例子，如yaz</blockquote><br />\n我食緊yaz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n謝謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都係幫返樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f799bd83e2d1bf21c048eb353bba7a35a4901db9","tid":179933,"uid":71467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"之前睇醫生話避孕藥要食夠三個月先穩陣"},{"pid":"8fa7271e32d9a1eb72744ffc15038e9dfb09d952","tid":179933,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:17:48.000Z","msg":"完全睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我男人黎 唔駛食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab03a0781134776364e2cf70808af85455f3955","tid":179933,"uid":95582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"試下食事後藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43c051b39f85b56749dc7e547e62f3239b7dca40","tid":179933,"uid":90546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"家計會幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846a19c14d8a5c40573fd483a3e7f1f1da44d856","tid":179933,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T11:26:40.000Z","msg":"你自己唔識食要人餵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=